column20: Mode of waste transport (road, rail, air, sea, or inland waterway)
column21: Expected waste collection date (only use numbers and slashes between the day, month and year, for example 13/01/25)
column22: Receiver  authorisation type (permit, licence, regulatory position statement, or other local agreement)
column23: Receiver  environmental permit number or waste exepmtion number (if applicable)
